Upload Image

 

To upload a Image:

  1. Select the Create / Upload button
  2. Select the context you want the Image to be uploaded

    Note: You can upload the Image in the context of a cultural object or in the context of project or any folder. Uploading an Image in the context of another system objects means that this Image will be part of that context and the permissions on that Image will depend on this context.

     

  3. Select "Upload" option
  4. Select "Select file.." option and chose the file from you local drive
  5. "Image" as a type will be recognized automatically if you are uploading png, jpg, tiff file types.
  6. Select the Image type you want to be uploaded. 
  7. Fill in the title
  8. Select Upload
  9. The Image landing page will be opened where you can fill the Image data and save.
